reviewText: I love all four movies and have been looking for three of them everyone. So happy about this purchase.

I had kind of remembered seeing the movie "12 Monkeys" when the TV series of the same name came on.  That is why I ordered this DVD so I could compare with the series.  I have to say the TV series has the nod from me over the movie with Bruce Willis.  The movie had too many unanswered questions and the TV series has more ways to go with the subject.
My hubby loved this for Christmas!

I purchased this specifically for "12 Monkeys," and received 3 extra movies as a bonus!  All four look great, and the "12 Monkeys" image and sound quality is outstanding.  Plus, all 4 DVDs come in one case only slightly thicker than a standard DVD case, which is very convenient and space saving.
What can I say, it's a four pack dvd set, works as it should.
Wanted the movie children of men because my husband has never seen it. Got that and three more!
You have to be out there to watch. Thanks to my wife.
All four movies are great to watch.
Some of the best in sci fi. In my opinion, Brad Pitt's best supporting role!
This DVD was worth the price for 12 Monkeys, can't say I enjoyed Children of Men because it was hard to understand what they were saying. Repo Men was good, and I haven't watched Doomsday yet.
Movies were all in great condition!
Can't beat the price.  Worth it for Twelve Monkeys alone.
